reviews.review_text: Really Nice Hadn't heard this show since I witnessed it live. Really brings back memories. I was 10ft in front of the board on the floor and it sounded great and this recording really did it justice. Nice Job Dude! One of the earlier Bianoral recordings i have heard and a fine one indeed!

My first show--Dear Mr. Fantasy sealed the deal Excellent recording, Mike! This was my first show; went along with my late friend, Art "Hippie" Vitti. Brent's heavenly version of Dear Mr. Fantasy sealed the deal on an already great show and made me a Dead Head. Brought some tears to my eyes hearing this again, Thank You!
Still going Furthur; saw 12/30/10 in San Francisco and looking forward to Furthur at the Greek Theatre, Los Angeles later this summer.
